========================================================
Install OgitorPhysicsPlugin on Debian
////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

1.Get Ogre SDK (1.7 recommend)
2.Get Ogitor source package
3.Compile Ogitor
    http://www.ogitor.org/Building+Ogitor?tikiversion=Linux
4.cd to the OgitorPhysicsPlugin directory
5.Edit ./build.sh .Change the header search path.
6.Run ./build.sh
7.Copy the "Media" and "Plugins" folders to your Ogitor directory

========================================================
